    "body": "It would be nice to have the ability to remove all implicit packages that are not needed anymore since the explicit package that requested them is already uninstalled\r\n\r\n### Rationale\r\n\r\nThis would be really helpful to keep the list of installed packages tidy and save memory space\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nI could image extending the `spack clean` command to support such an action.\r\nBut also introducing a new command like `spack reclaim` (inspired by macports) would be an option.\r\n",
